                    <div class="card mt-4 border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8e1 0%, #ffecb3 100%);">
                        <div class="card-body p-4 text-center">
                            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2 text-warning"><i class="bi bi-gift-fill me-2"></i> »—š«„Ő «Š„Ŗ«›¬ </h5>
                            <p class="text-muted small mb-3">ř„ »Ōŕś… 5 ›šŪŪš ŠŠ ”ŐŪŠ ś śňŪř Õ”«»« Ś„ (»‘Ś«Ō… ő»—…) ś«—»Õ <strong>500 Ő.„</strong>  ÷«› Š„Õ›Ŕ Ŗ ›ś—«ū!</p>
                            <div class="bg-white rounded-pill py-2 px-3 d-inline-block border border-warning shadow-sm">
                                <span class="fw-bold text-dark me-2">ŖśŌ «ŠŌŕś… «Šő«’ »Ŗ:</span>
